ame\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Matroid/Minor/Contract.html#Matroid.contract\"><span class=\"name\">Matroid</span>.<span class=\"name\">contract</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Matroid/Basic.html#Matroid\">Matroid</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Matroid/Basic.html#Matroid\">Matroid</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The contraction `M ／ C` is the matroid on `M.E \\ C` in which a set `I ⊆ M.E \\ C` is independent\nif and only if `I ∪ J` is independent, where `J` is an arbitrarily chosen basis for `C`.\nIt is also equal by definition to `(M✶ ＼ C)✶`; see `Matroid.IsBasis.contract_indep_iff` for\na proof that its independent sets are the claimed ones. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Matroid/Minor/Contract.html#Matroid.contract","kind":"def","line":57,"name":"Matroid.contract","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Combinatorics/Matroid/Minor/Contract.lean#L57-L61"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Combinatorics.Matroid.Minor.Delete","Mathlib.Tactic.TautoSet"],"instances":[{"className":"Matroid.Finite","name":"Matroid.contract_finite","typeNames":["Matroid.contract"]},{"className":"Matroid.RankFinite","name":"Matroid.contract_rankFinite","typeNames":["Matroid.contract"]},{"className":"Matroid.Finitary","name":"Matroid.contract_finitary","typeNames":["Matroid.contract"]}],"name":"Mathlib.Combinatorics.Matroid.Minor.Contract"}